{"tid":509990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯真係好hea","createTime":"2017-12-26T03:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T08:52:05.000Z","uid":6582,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"233b33f2d22d2dcaa010332db1929c7b53c4b6a3","tid":509990,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"包你估唔到！　美斯喺國家打吡做啲乜？<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171226&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57627207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171226%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57627207&d=uBAeJpYWmU%2Bax4UVActdkC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=716a4837\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171226%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57627207&h=b4d9d86a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171226&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57627207</a><br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿上禮拜六喺西甲國家打吡作客巴拿比奴贏皇家馬德里3:0，前鋒美斯喺呢場大戰入一粒，兼有一次助攻，係巴塞表現最好嘅其中一位球員。不過，最誇張嘅係，美斯嘅表現雖然係舉足輕重，但原來呢位阿根廷國家隊隊長成場波幾乎無跑過咁滯，一直都係行行企企。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《馬卡報》報道，根據統計數字，喺國家打吡踢足90分鐘嘅美斯，超過八成嘅時間係喺度行緊，足足有83.1%嘅時間。其餘時間，美斯嘅速度有10.8%係慢跑緊，真正跑緊嘅時間係4.95%，另外果1.15%嘅就係全速跑緊，即係大約有一分鐘左右。不過講番轉頭，美斯係巴塞今季唯一踢足所有西甲賽事嘅外場球員，咁梗係要識得留力喇，唔通下下死衝咩？"},{"pid":"8903f11e0de07ff84d28fe7ae2b89210647d7d04","tid":509990,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"咁HEA都咁好表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3c25e930aa86eb5e6cda16e811c7ffd19ef315","tid":509990,"uid":90422,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"真係垃圾 仲話球王<br />\n牙朗先係球王"},{"pid":"f200aea270951063ecbffa4b0dd0e56558bdb4a6","tid":509990,"uid":27777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"留力都踢贏牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb5b8533def4d81f8aa0efe60f25f5e5917f16b","tid":509990,"uid":30040,